info.description:
This archive contains the distribution WWW_RottenTomatoes,
version 1.0.0:

  A Python interface to the Rotten Tomatoes API

  This module is intended to provide an interface between
  Python and the Rotten Tomatoes JSON API. The Rotten Tomatoes
  API is a RESTful web service. In order to use this library
  you must provide an api key which requires registration.
  For more information please see http://dev.rottentomatoes.com

This software is copyright (c) 2011 by Casey Vega and
released under the GNU GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE.
